aa(lp250
VIn this plot I'm showing you at what pay rate people stopped.
p251
aVSo low numbers mean that people worked harder.
p252
aVThey worked for much longer.
p253
aVIn the acknowledged condition,
p254
aVpeople worked all the way down to 15 cents.
p255
