aVNow you could say \u2014 if you were a builder,
p369
aVdo you think [you'd say], "Oh, I love this origami,
p370
aVbut I know that nobody else would love it?"
p371
aVOr "I love this origami, and everybody else will love it as well?"
p372
aVWhich one of those two is correct?
